Detailed Description

A batch record.

Contains an array of characters, an array of ints and an array of floats. 

typedef struct umtz_bat_ {
  char  cdata[3*MTZRECLEN];
  int   idata[MTZBATINT];
  float fdata[MTZBATFLT];
} umtz_bat;
